response.overview: On March 9th GCW: Ashes to Ashes 2024 is live on TrillerTV+ straight from Showboat in Atlantic City, NJ. The event features the GCW Tag Team Title Match where Violence Is Forever (Dominic Garrini & Kevin Ku) defend their titles against Dark Sheik & Sawyer Wreck.  Also in the lineup:  John Wayne Murdoch vs Brandon Kirk  Tag Team Match  Mr. Danger & Terry Yaki vs Los Macizos (Ciclope & Miedo Extremo)  Tag Team Match  Blake Christian & Shane Mercer vs Gahbage Daddies (Alec Price & Cole Radrick)  Tony Deppen vs Microman  Danhausen vs Charles Mason  Nick Gage vs Ryuji Ito  Abdullah Kobayashi vs Matt Tremont  Atlantic City Strap Match  Effy vs Mance Warner
response.title: GCW Ashes to Ashes 2024
